# SEO & Web Performance

## Metadata
- Static pages: export `metadata` di `page.tsx`
- Dynamic (`/shop/[slug]`): `generateMetadata` dengan nama, deskripsi, gambar → OpenGraph
- Semua halaman wajib punya fallback brand BARBARA

## Structured Data
- Product detail: JSON-LD (`application/ld+json`) — name, image, description, SKU, offers (price, currency, availability)
- Katalog & detail produk: BreadcrumbList schema

## Sitemap & Robots
- `src/app/sitemap.ts`: rute statis + dynamic product slugs dari DB
- `src/app/robots.ts`: allow katalog; block `/cart`, `/checkout`, `/account/*`, `/admin/*`

## Images
- Wajib `next/image` — dilarang `<img>` kecuali inline SVG kecil
- Set `sizes` presisi per viewport
- WebP/AVIF via Next.js; `priority` pada hero homepage & main product image (LCP)

## Rendering Strategy
| Strategy | Halaman |
|----------|---------|
| ISR (`revalidate: 3600`) | `/shop`, `/shop/[slug]` |
| SSR | Cart, Checkout, Account, Admin |
| Server Components | Layout & page containers default |
| `"use client"` | Hanya elemen interaktif (hooks, state, context) |
